<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. Als du uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Jacob <expan>Topl<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> rede <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die er
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        süll, darumb <add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> wir in cze rede
                        gesaczt und er hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> rede <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        dir nicht getan hab. Nu getrawen wir dir wol, du sicherst
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> auf frewntlich recht. Hetst du
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czü im iht <expan>cze
                            sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>sch<ex>ein</ex>bot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>von im</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> hie vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                        wenn wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist. Und ob du im
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> iht tetst, so gescheh im
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir ungütlich.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> Marie xi. </ab>
</div>
